OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F381A1774800665
OL,3,CTeam Jets secure Premier League
OL,4,Cpromotion
OL,6,FTeam Jets have celebrated a landmark
OL,7,Fwin as the Jersey netball team has
OL,8,Fsecured a Premier League promotion
OL,9,Ffollowing a 59-53 win against Norfolk
OL,10,FUnited today.
OL,12,FThe Evelyn Partners Jets will now
OL,13,Fadvance to the Premier League 2, the
OL,14,Fthird tier of English netball.
OL,16,FCo-head Coach Emily Green, says: "This
OL,17,Fis massive for us, making Premier
OL,18,FLeague 3 was huge for us, but making
OL,19,FPremier League 2 shows not only can we
OL,20,Fplay, but we can dominate certain
OL,21,Fteams at the Premiership level."
OL,1,W~+$z5~{4~k4~k4~sj5  hws         G1/7
OL,2,W+.!/*%/*%/*%/*%+,"-$ /(,'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BCh Is News CThis Day FReg TV
FL,382,380,120,260,000,100
PN,38102
SC,0002
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F381A1774800665
OL,3,CTeam Jets secure Premier League
OL,4,Cpromotion
OL,6,FShe continues: "This is a big one for
OL,7,Fus today. We knew we had a target to
OL,8,Freach, but we didn't want that to
OL,9,Fchange how we attacked the game and
OL,10,Fwhat has been working for us all
OL,11,Fseason."
OL,13,F"This is such a lovely way to see off
OL,14,Fwhat has been such a successful season
OL,15,Ffor us."
OL,17,FCommenting on the game, Emily admits
OL,18,Fit was a tricky start, she explains:
OL,19,F"Nerves were there, so we took a bit
OL,20,Fof time to figure some bits out.
OL,1,W~+$z5~{4~k4~k4~sj5  hws         G2/7
OL,2,W+.!/*%/*%/*%/*%+,"-$ /(,'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BCh Is News CThis Day FReg TV
FL,382,380,120,260,000,100
PN,38103
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F381A1774800665
OL,3,CTeam Jets secure Premier League
OL,4,Cpromotion
OL,6,F"We are such a resilient team, and the
OL,7,Fteam has built such resilience from
OL,8,Fbattling to get up to the playoffs,
OL,9,Fand we have also had tight games all
OL,10,Fseason, so that resilience has paid
OL,11,Foff today."
OL,13,FEmily adds: "This will show girls in
OL,14,FJersey, you're on an island, there
OL,15,Faren't many of us, but our programme
OL,16,Fis good, do the hard work, have
OL,17,Fdiscipline, and you can get where you
OL,18,Fwant to be."
OL,1,W~+$z5~{4~k4~k4~sj5  hws         G3/7
OL,2,W+.!/*%/*%/*%/*%+,"-$ /(,'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BCh Is News CThis Day FReg TV
FL,382,380,120,260,000,100
PN,38104
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F381A1774800665
OL,3,CTeam Jets secure Premier League
OL,4,Cpromotion
OL,6,FTeam captain, Rosie Tonner, says: "We
OL,7,Fknew this was going to be a big game
OL,8,Fand that Norfolk had nothing to lose,
OL,9,Fbut we had it all to lose, so we are
OL,10,Fdelighted.
OL,12,F"We didn't get off to the best of a
OL,13,Fstart, we were down by nine or 10
OL,14,Fgoals at one point in the second
OL,15,Fquater, but to come back in that
OL,16,Fsecond half shows what resilience the
OL,17,Fgirls have had all season.
OL,19,F"Our experience and composure really
OL,20,Fpulled it off today.
OL,1,W~+$z5~{4~k4~k4~sj5  hws         G4/7
OL,2,W+.!/*%/*%/*%/*%+,"-$ /(,'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BCh Is News CThis Day FReg TV
FL,382,380,120,260,000,100
PN,38105
SC,0005
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F381A1774800665
OL,3,CTeam Jets secure Premier League
OL,4,Cpromotion
OL,6,F"When we came into the Premier League
OL,7,F3, we thought we just wanted to
OL,8,Fcompete because we didn't know what
OL,9,Fthe level of competition was going to
OL,10,Fbe like.
OL,12,F"It got to about halfway through the
OL,13,Fseason, and we realised actually we
OL,14,Fcan do this."
OL,1,W~+$z5~{4~k4~k4~sj5  hws         G5/7
OL,2,W+.!/*%/*%/*%/*%+,"-$ /(,'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BCh Is News CThis Day FReg TV
FL,382,380,120,260,000,100
PN,38106
SC,0006
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F381A1774800665
OL,3,CTeam Jets secure Premier League
OL,4,Cpromotion
OL,6,FRosie says it has not been an easy
OL,7,Fjourney, she explains: "There was a
OL,8,Flot of rebuilding we had to do to get
OL,9,Fhere. We have worked so hard to get
OL,10,Fhere, we had to go through three play-
OL,11,Foffs to get to Premier League 3, and
OL,12,Fto be here in Premier League 2 is
OL,13,Fmassive for the island.
OL,15,F"Hopefully, this inspires youngsters
OL,16,Fto play netball."
OL,1,W~+$z5~{4~k4~k4~sj5  hws         G6/7
